WEBVTT

00:00:28.520 --> 00:00:32.456
Biološki ritam određuje
našu razinu energije tijekom dana,

00:00:32.479 --> 00:00:37.336
a tek nedavno smo proveli
globalno testiranje ovog ritma,

00:00:37.360 --> 00:00:39.416
koji ugrožava zdravlje našeg sna,

00:00:39.440 --> 00:00:42.840
kao i kvalitetu našeg života.

00:00:44.240 --> 00:00:45.496
Zbog toga,

00:00:45.520 --> 00:00:47.656
ne spavamo koliko bismo trebali,

00:00:47.680 --> 00:00:51.416
prosječan Amerikanac spava puni sat manje

00:00:51.440 --> 00:00:53.936
nego u 1940-ima.

00:00:53.960 --> 00:00:55.216
Iz nekog razloga,

00:00:55.240 --> 00:00:57.496
odlučili smo se ponositi time

00:00:57.520 --> 00:00:59.760
što možemo izdržati bez dovoljno sna.